                            <a href="http://www.health24.com/Medical/Incontinence/From-our-sponsors/incontinence-and-depression-20170901">8 strategies for treating both your bladder problems and your depression</a>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                    <figure>
                        <a Height="125" Width="145" href="http://www.health24.com/Medical/IBS/From-our-sponsors/identifying-what-triggers-your-ibs-20170808"><img src="https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/General/d/6046/450c6b1c7db347628ac17fc6242a210c.jpg" alt="" /></a>           
